longBusinessSummary: SMT Scharf AG plans, produces, sells, installs, and maintains machinery and equipment for the transportation of personnel, equipment, and material for underground mining and tunnel construction. The company operates through Coal Mining, Mineral Mining, Tunnel, and Other Industries segments. It offers diesel-powered monorail locomotives, electrical monorail transport systems, chairlift systems, segment cranes, construction site cranes, explosive device placement device, drilling and splitting device, aerial work platform, walking beam, lifting beam, lifting bar, miniclimber, and rope drive. Its products are primarily used in hard coal, gold, platinum, copper, nickel, hard rock, and salt mining activities. The company has operations in Germany, Russia and other CIS states, Poland, China, Africa, the United States, and internationally. SMT Scharf AG was founded in 1941 and is based in Hamm, Germany.
